data.description:
This Beautiful Ranch style home Located in Hoffman Heights, has tons of natural lighting, 3 spacious bedrooms and has a bright open floor plan throughout the living room and kitchen. Vinyl Flooring and Carpet, Granite countertops and well kept appliances! Sellers recently replaced the dryer, Water heater is newer, It was replaced in January 2023.(All appliances included with sale). It’s about 5-7 min away from Anschutz Medical Campus. Close walk to Local Restaurants & Del mar pool. The home has Huge back yard with a back shed for extra storage and a large covered patio!! NO HOA FEES 

No Showings on weekends due to personal reasons. 
Seller is not willing to negotiate any repairs, this home Repairs on the foundation. 

Don’t wait, make this home yours!
